Package: ggtricks
Title: Create Sector and Other Charts Easily Using Grammar of Graphics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Abdoul", "ISSA BIDA", , "contact@abdoulblog.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of several geom to create graphics, using
    "ggplot2" and the Cartesian coordinate system. You use the familiar
    mapping 'Grammar of Graphics' without the need to do another
    transformation into polar cordinates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/AbdoulMa/ggtricks
BugReports: https://github.com/AbdoulMa/ggtricks/issues
Imports: 
    cli,
    ggplot2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
